			<div class="atl-item" _host="zhangjun02" id="5" replyid="4939379" js_username="zhangjun02" js_resTime="2004-04-02 12:21:00">
				<div class="atl-head" id="6179795379c9738fe8bdf65b93714bc4">
					<div class="atl-head-reply"></div>
					<div class="atl-info">
						<span>作者：<a href="http://www.tianya.cn/210464" target="_blank" class="js-vip-check" uid="210464" uname="zhangjun02">zhangjun02</a> </span>
						<span>时间：2004-04-02 12:21:00</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="atl-content">
					<div class="atl-con-hd clearfix">
						<div class="atl-con-hd-l"></div>
						<div class="atl-con-hd-r"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="atl-con-bd clearfix">
						<div class="bbs-content">
							　　有时，制作一部电影的费用能抵一个国家研究所一年的运营成本。<br>　　<br>　　<br>
							
						</div>
						<div class="atl-reply">
							
							<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="reportme a-link" replyid="4939379" replytime="2004-04-02 12:21:00" author="zhangjun02" authorId="210464">举报</a> |
							<a name="4939379" href="javascript:void(0);" class="mark a-link">收藏</a> |							
							<span>5楼</span> |
							<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="a-link-2 ir-shang" floor="5">
								打赏
							</a> |
							<a class="a-link-2 reply" href="#fabu_anchor">回复</a> |
